Isannah Lapham is the youngest daughter of Mrs. Lapham. Isannah is selfish and vain, and beloved by Cilla. Isannahâ€™s golden-haired, ethereal beauty attracts a great deal of attention, most significantly from Lavinia Lyte. Lavinia takes Isannah into her care and introduces her to high society, separating her from her family and their lower-class ways of life.